1978;;In Praise of Older Women;;Canadian;;George Kaczender;;Tom Berenger, Karen Black, Susan Strasberg;;drama based on the novel by stephen vizinczey;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/In_Praise_of_Older_Women_(1978_film);;Andras Vayda (Tom Berenger) grows up in a turbulent, war-torn Hungary, where he procures local girls for the occupying G.I.s during World War II. Disappointed by the girls his age, he meets Maya (Karen Black), a married woman in her 30s, who tutors him in love and romance. Maya is only the first of many mature women whom Andras will meet through his teenage and young adult life.